   Flight Planning

   This links below provide access to two tables to help users with their
   flight planning. They allow the user to determine the appropriate
   flying height to get the desired swath width and pixel size. The range
   of flying heights available depends on the platform. For more
   information on the platforms that MASTER can be operated from see
   Sensor and Platform

